QueryParameter - Class in core.tut.pori.http.parameters
The default parser for query parameters, the syntax being: ?query=VALUE It is also possible to provide query for a specific type with ?query=TYPE:VALUE The two variations can be combined: ?query=TYPE;VALUE,VALUE The order of parameter values is preserved.
